  <h3 itemprop="name">Bagaimana doa buka puasa yang benar atau Sahih?</h3>
  <div itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
    <div itemprop="text">
      <p>Doa buka puasa yang dicontohkan atau disunnahkan oleh Rasulullah (saw) adalah:</p>

      <p>(1) <em>Allahumma laka shumtu wa ‘alaa rizqika afthortu</em> [<sup id="fnref:hds-601ca775-f1a4-4841-82b4-9d03d719a163" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:hds-601ca775-f1a4-4841-82b4-9d03d719a163" class="footnote">1</a></sup>] dan (2) <em>Dzahabazh-zhoma-u wabtallatil ‘uruqu wa tsabatal ajru insyaa Allah</em> [<sup id="fnref:hds-648a1e90-9d4b-4394-87b5-8d4fa59a6d37" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:hds-648a1e90-9d4b-4394-87b5-8d4fa59a6d37" class="footnote">2</a></sup>]</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

